Name: polycystic kidney disease 4
Definition: A autosomal recessive polycystic kidney disease that has_material_basis_in mutation in the PKD4 gene.
Synonym: Primary mediastinal clear cell lymphoma of B-cell type

Name: polycystic kidney disease 5
Definition: A autosomal recessive polycystic kidney disease that has_material_basis_in autosomal dominant inheritance of homozygous mutation in the DZIP1L gene on chromosome 3q22.
